ams-review-netflix-3532889">“ Robbie Williams”评论：Netflix Doc清楚地表明了流行明星的危险</a></strong></li></ul><p>英国流行音乐偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3553493">将于7月6日（星期六）登台</a>，此前宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andrea-bocelli-announced-first-headline-act-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3535927">头条新闻安德里亚·博塞利（Andrea Bocelli），后者将在周五（7月5日）上映</a>。</p><p>英国夏季表演将是这位歌手的英国独家，他将在那里表演“摇滚DJ”，“让我娱乐您”和“天使”等热门歌曲。</p><p>宣布威廉姆斯约会的其他客人包括肖恩·赖德（Shaun Ryder）的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-grape">黑葡萄</a>，詹姆斯·史密斯（James Smith），埃尔（Ellur），达维娜·米歇尔（Davina Michelle），瑞安·吉布（Ryan Gibb）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ben-kidson">本·柴顿（Ben Kidson）</a> 。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Frobbie-williams-tickets%2Fartist%2F783976" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处购买剩余的门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3767744" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3767744" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3767744" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="罗比·威廉姆斯BST海德公园海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Robbie-Williams-BST-Hyde-Park-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 